- I'm on it.

37:26.619 --> 37:29.664
And, uh,
hey, how about a real drink, huh?

37:29.664 --> 37:30.748
As in, booze?

37:30.748 --> 37:33.292
I don't think you're old enough
to be drinking, D.

37:33.292 --> 37:35.253
Who cares? You own the place.

37:35.253 --> 37:36.462
Come on.

37:36.462 --> 37:38.506
Hook a brother up
with a Long Island iced tea.

37:38.506 --> 37:39.882
Who's gonna know?

37:40.299 --> 37:41.509
I will.

37:42.093 --> 37:44.262
Besides, I told your mom
I'm watching out for you.

37:44.262 --> 37:46.889
