39:18.022 --> 39:21.442
Well, you know,
France warned the U.S. government

39:21.442 --> 39:23.611
because of their experience with Algeria.

39:24.445 --> 39:27.406
And then told them
that maybe this was not a good idea.

39:28.324 --> 39:30.951
And they didn't want
to send their people to die.

39:31.869 --> 39:35.706
Listen, I, I don't get why
you want to do a book about 9/11

39:36.499 --> 39:38.334
if this is your take on America.

39:38.334 --> 39:40.628
Because it's an amazing story.

39:40.628 --> 39:44.590
It's a story about
how so many people in the world

39:44.590 --> 39:47.093
came to support America and its people.

39:47.093 --> 39:50.304
